{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/Poetry/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Passerby's Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9a7048f7-c5c9-5b25-b54f-7e0f55e107c1","excerpt":"徐志摩的一首小诗，偶然，写于192…","html":"<p>徐志摩的一首小诗，偶然，写于1926年五月。浪漫主义，相当的浪漫主义。</p>\n<p><em>徐志摩</em></p>\n<p>我是天空里的一片云，</p>\n<p>偶尔投影在你的波心――</p>\n<p>你不必讶异，</p>\n<p>更无须欢喜――</p>\n<p>在转瞬间消灭了踪影。</p>\n<p>你我相逢在黑夜的海上，</p>\n<p>你有你的，我有我的，方向；</p>\n<p>你记得也好，</p>\n<p>最好你忘掉，</p>\n<p>在这交会时互放的光亮！\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/ec9575b00307e26b39d4a7c043dae1f1/fcda8/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ec9575b00307e26b39d4a7c043dae1f1/12f09/1.png 148w,\n/static/ec9575b00307e26b39d4a7c043dae1f1/e4a3f/1.png 295w,\n/static/ec9575b00307e26b39d4a7c043dae1f1/fcda8/1.png 590w,\n/static/ec9575b00307e26b39d4a7c043dae1f1/efc66/1.png 885w,\n/static/ec9575b00307e26b39d4a7c043dae1f1/c83ae/1.png 1180w,\n/static/ec9575b00307e26b39d4a7c043dae1f1/21b4d/1.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>  偶然看到这首偶然的诗歌，我也不必惊讶，也不必欢喜。那就这样，平平常常的记录一下。</p>","fields":{"slug":"/Poetry/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"偶然","date":"2020-06-20T00:00:00.000Z","description":"徐志摩的一首小诗，偶然，写于1926年五月。浪漫主义，相当的浪漫主义"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Poetry/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/graduation/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Graduated"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/Long-termi